Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为知情而遭到解雇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sacked for the crime of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉这些被精挑细选出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you think that these scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁观一场走过场性质的庭审的科学家们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}handpicked to witness a show trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会受我影响而行动起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will somehow be stirred into action by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我违抗国家  采取了英勇的立场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because of some heroic stance I take in defiance of the State?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没错  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是瓦列利·列加索夫  你的话有份量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you're Valery Legasov, and you mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望如果我把事实说出来就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to think that if I spoke out, it would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道这世界的规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I know how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会枪毙我的  霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They will shoot me, Khomyuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我查清楚真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You told me to find out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找数十人谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I spoke to dozens of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记下了他们说的每一个字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every word they said, I wrote down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在这些笔记本里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All in these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是还活着的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the ones who are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是已经死了的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the ones who are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为救彼此而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They died rescuing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为灭火而死  为照顾伤者而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Putting out fires, tending to the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有犹豫  也没有动摇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They didn't hesitate, they didn't waiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做了必须做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They simply did what had to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自愿接近暴露的反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I went willingly to an open reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我已经献出了生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I've already given my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还不够吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉  但那还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I'm sorry, but it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(2500,0)\c&HF9FFFF&\pos(191.2,155.188)}切尔诺贝利市\N1987年7月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联共产党中央委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Central Committee of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及苏联最高苏维埃主席团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the Presidium of the Supreme Soviet of the U.S.S.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定代表人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has determined that justice be carried out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸张正义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on behalf of the People
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这符合由第二十届  二十一届\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in accordance with the general goal of our Party
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十二届代表大会所制定的我党总目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as determined by its 20th, 21st, and 22nd Congresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即列宁主义目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which is a Leninist goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论以前  现在或将来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was, is, and will be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是苏联唯一不变的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the only immutable goal in the Soviet state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要坚定不移地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The path of Leninist principles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走马列主义原则道路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}shall be consistently and undeviatingly followed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这体现了苏维埃人民的切身利益\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as it expresses the vital interests of the Soviet People,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望与决心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}its hopes and aspirations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如它指导了党和国家的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as we guide the life of the Party and the State.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本庭开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This session of court is now open,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由米兰·卡德尼考夫法官同志主审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Judge Milan Kadnikov presiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indictments:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多·布卡诺夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Viktor Bryukhanov,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安纳托利·迪亚特洛夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anatoly Dyatlov,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼克莱·福明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nikolai Fomin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违反苏联刑法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are accused of violating Article 220 Section 2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二章第220条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Criminal Code of the Soviet Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致1986年4月26日发生核灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}resulting in a nuclear disaster on April 26, 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检方传唤霍缪克同志出庭作证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The State calls witnesses Comrade Khomyuk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来自白俄罗斯核能源研究所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Byelorussian Nuclear Institute,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有库尔恰托夫原子能研究所的列加索夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Legasov of the Kurchatov Institute of Atomic Energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鲍里斯·埃夫多基莫维奇·谢比纳同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Comrade Boris Evdokimovich Shcherbina,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长理事会的副主席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Deputy Chairman of the Council of Ministers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼燃料与能源局局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and head of the Bureau for Fuel and Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切从一场安全测试开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It began with, of all things, a safety test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初为什么需要做安全测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why was there need for a safety test at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事故发生时  4号反应堆已经不新了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reactor Number 4 was not new when the accident occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  它是在1983年12月20日投入使用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, it went into operation on December 20th, 1983.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11天后  就在那年的最后一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eleven days later, on the last day of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核电站厂长维克多·布卡诺夫签下这份文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plant Director Viktor Bryukhanov signed this document--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证实反应堆施工工程完工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}certifying the completion of the construction of the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于赶在年前结束工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As a result of finishing the work before the end of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布卡诺夫同志被授予社会主义劳动英雄称号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Bryukhanov was awarded Hero of Socialist Labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福明同志被授予勇敢奖章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Fomin was awarded for Valorous Labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫同志被授予红旗勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Dyatlov was given an Order of the Red Banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们的工作尚未完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But their work was not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份文件是伪造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this document was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签署证书之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In order to sign this certificate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须成功完成所有安全测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all safety tests had to have been successfully completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而有一项未完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and yet, one remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核反应堆中的堆芯会产生热量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A nuclear reactor generates heat in the core here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有多台水泵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A series of pumps, here and here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以恒定流量驱动冷却水流过堆芯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}send a constant flow of cooling water through the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆芯的热量将水转化为蒸汽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The core's heat turns the water to steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒸汽推动汽轮机转动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the steam spins the turbine here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而产生电能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the result is electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果一座电厂失去动力会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what if a power plant has no power?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果电厂本身的供电中断会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if the power feeding the plant itself is disrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停电  设备故障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A blackout, equipment failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者遭到外敌袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or an attack by a foreign enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有电力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's no power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泵就无法向堆芯供水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the pumps cannot move water through the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有水  堆芯就会过热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And without water, the core overheats,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料会熔毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the fuel melts down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简而言之  核灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In short, a nuclear disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有三台柴油备用发电机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three diesel fuel backup generators here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题解决了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, problem solved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布卡诺夫知道问题根本没有解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bryukhanov knew that the problem was not solved at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,备用发电机需要一分钟左右\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The backup generators took approximately one minute
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能达到所需转速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to reach the speed required
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱动水泵  避免堆芯熔毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to power the pumps and prevent a meltdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时  一切都晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and by that time, it would be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面就来说说安全测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we arrive at the safety test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理论如下  如果设备失去供电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The theory was this: If the facility lost power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在转动的汽轮机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the turbine, which had been spinning,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会经过一段时间的减速  最终停机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would take some time to slow down and stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能将这段时间之内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if you could take the electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它所发出的电能输送给水泵呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it was still generating and transfer it to the pumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果正在惰转的汽轮机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if the dying turbine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够驱动水泵运行足够长的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}could keep the pumps working long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以填补发电机投入前的60秒缺口呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to bridge the 60-second gap until the generators came on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  请继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Continue, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了测试这一理论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To test this theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将反应堆置于低功率模式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the reactor is placed in a reduced power mode--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,700兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}700 megawatts--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以模拟停电状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to simulate a blackout condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随后使汽轮机停运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then the turbines are turned off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在转速逐渐降低的过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and as they slowly spin down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测量其电力输出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}their electrical output is measured
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判断是否足以驱动水泵运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to see if it's enough to power the pumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学理论没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The science is strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际效果取决于执行测试的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but a test is only as good as the men carrying it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的第一次测试失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, the first time they tried, they failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次测试失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The second time they tried, they failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三次测试失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The third time they tried, they failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fourth time they tried
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在1986年4月26日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was April 26th, 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍缪克同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Khomyuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要理解那晚发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To understand what happened that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回到10小时之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have to go back ten hours earlier--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到4月25日  安全测试本该展开的当天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}April 25th, the day the test was meant to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午两点钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By two in the afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应堆的功率已经减少一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the reactor has been lowered by half
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从正常的3200兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from its normal output level of 3200 megawatts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降到1600兆瓦并保持稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to 1600 megawatts and is stable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且已准备好把功率降低到测试要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and ready to be reduced to its final output level for the test:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,700兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}700 megawatts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在他们继续之前  来了一个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But before they can proceed, there is a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基辅的电网官员说在午夜之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Power grid officials in Kiev say that they cannot afford
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不能承受电力供应的进一步降低了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a further reduction in the electricity until after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要求把测试推后十个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They are asking for a ten-hour delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第一个关键时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the first critical moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾难的连锁反应的第一环\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the first link in the chain of disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称职的管理团队肯定会坚持把测试取消\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Competent management would have insisted on canceling the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这三个人却同意让测试继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These three men allowed it to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么推后会如此危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why was this delay so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它造成了两个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It created two problems:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是科学问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of them is scientific in nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个则是人员问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the other is very human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先考虑这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the one we will consider first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午夜有个交接班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At midnight, there is a shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}切尔诺贝利\N弗拉基米尔·伊里奇·列宁核电站
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-霍登楚克  -别想了  你找别人去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Khodemchuk-- - Forget it. Find another fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托普特诺夫  想买辆摩托车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Toptunov, want to buy a motorcycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托普特诺夫  他还是个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Toptunov? He's just a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他脸上的毛比底下的还多呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's got more hair on his face than on his balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛  他嘴唇上是毛吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hair? Is that what's on his lip?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列尼德·费罗维奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leonid Fedorovych.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫让你尽快去控制室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov says to come to the control room as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他已经到了  -他来得早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is he already here? - He came in early.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于测试的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something about a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了吧  像什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see? Desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨沙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们本该做的那个测试吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ah. You know the test they were supposed to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断电后汽轮机惰性发电  他们去年做过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The turbine rundown, they tried it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没办法在白班做  所以就交给我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They couldn't do it on the day shift, so they've given it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't know what--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们根本不知道测试怎么做  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We don't know what it is. - It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把热功率降到700  保持住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We take it down to 700, hold it there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交给斯托利楚克还有科什鲍姆  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the rest is Stolyarchuk and Kirschenbaum, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫会来监督\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dyatlov is gonna be supervising.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做件从来没做过的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to do something I've never done before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:23:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且迪亚特洛夫还要在身后盯着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with Dyatlov looking over my shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  我们一起来完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, well, don't worry, we'll do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在看操作指示呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm looking at the instructions now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要做那些吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are we supposed to do those or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我是4号反应堆的阿基莫夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, this is Akimov in 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手上有惰性发电测试的操作手册\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have the manual for the rundown test.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年你们做过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  程序里有如何操作的指示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, in the program there's instructions of what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有很多东西被划掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then, well, there's a lot of things crossed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What should I--?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what should I--?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.63,0:24:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说要我们按照被划掉的指示来操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He says to follow the crossed-out instructions.
