Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.08,0:25:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这样不对劲  -闭上嘴  好好干活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This is not good-- - Shut the fuck up and do your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.61,0:25:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托普特诺夫  把功率降到700兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Toptunov, reduce power to 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.83,0:25:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没在功率这么低的条件下操作过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never done this with the power so low before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.91,0:25:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我跟你一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's okay. I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.23,0:25:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在将功率降至700兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reducing power to 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请诸位想象一下尤里·加加林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to think of Yuri Gagarin.
