Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.51,0:26:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这就是当时4号反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is exactly what was happening
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.51,0:26:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制室里所发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the control room of Reactor 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.18,0:26:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜班的人并没有受过测试的训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The night shift had not been trained to perform the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.68,0:26:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至都没人通知他们会有这测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They hadn't even been warned it was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.48,0:26:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列尼德·托普特诺夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leonid Toptunov,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.53,0:26:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚负责控制和稳定反应堆的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the operator responsible for controlling and stabilizing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.19,0:26:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个操作员  他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the reactor that night was...
