Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是由延误造成的人员问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the human problem created by the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.56,0:26:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在反应堆堆芯里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But inside the reactor core,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在原子之间的空隙中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the space between the atoms themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.10,0:26:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有更加危险的东西在逐步形成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}something far more dangerous is forming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.74,0:26:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种毒素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.83,0:26:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是凌晨12时28分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The time is 28 past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.58,0:27:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Legasov.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.74,0:27:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴能在这儿见到一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm pleased to see some of my colleagues here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.28,0:27:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在库尔恰托夫原子能研究所和能源部的同事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the Kurchatov Institute and Minenergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.69,0:27:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是诸位不需要是核能科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you don't need to be a nuclear scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.39,0:28:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能理解切尔诺贝利发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to understand what happened at Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.65,0:28:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只需要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You only need to know this:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在核反应堆中基本上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there are essentially two things that happen
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.08,0:28:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只发生着两件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}inside a nuclear reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.11,0:28:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生核能的反应功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The reactivity which generates power
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.48,0:28:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然升高  要不然降低\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}either goes up, or it goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.84,0:28:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}升高
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.64,0:28:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}降低
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.48,0:28:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.19,0:28:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操作者只需要保持平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the operators do is maintain balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.20,0:28:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铀燃料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uranium fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.69,0:28:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}铀燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.55,0:28:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}铀燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.94,0:28:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铀原子分裂碰撞的时候  反应功率升高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As uranium atoms split apart and collide, reactivity goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.72,0:28:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果没有平衡好反应功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you don't balance the reactivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.70,0:28:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就会不断升高  所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it never stops rising. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.17,0:28:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}硼控制棒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.23,0:28:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硼控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Boron control rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.68,0:28:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们能够降低反应性  就像汽车的刹车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They reduce reactivity like brakes on a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.99,0:28:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还要考虑第三个因素  水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But there's a third factor to consider: water.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.68,0:28:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}水
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.13,0:28:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷水带走系统中的热量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cool water takes heat out of the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.68,0:28:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时水变成水蒸气  也是我们说的"空泡"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As it does, it turns to steam, or what we call a "void."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.20,0:29:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利核电站使用的RBMK反应堆中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In an RBMK reactor of the type used at Chernobyl,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.72,0:29:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个名词叫做"正空泡系数"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there's something called a "positive void coefficient."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.92,0:29:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.81,0:29:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着系统内的蒸汽含量越多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It means that the more steam present within the system,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.59,0:29:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}正空泡系数
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.11,0:29:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应性越高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the higher the reactivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.19,0:29:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着产生更多热量  意味着产生更多水蒸汽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which means more heat, which means more steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.14,0:29:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.40,0:29:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样似乎出现了恶性循环\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would appear we have a vicious cycle on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.94,0:29:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此  但还有...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we would, were it not for this--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we would,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.97,0:29:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were it not for this:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.76,0:29:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}负温度系数
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负温度系数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the negative temperature coefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.03,0:29:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当核燃料温度升高时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When nuclear fuel gets hotter,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.59,0:29:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应就会变缓  所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it gets less reactive, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.88,0:29:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料使反应性升高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}fuel increases reactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.55,0:29:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制棒和水能够使之降低\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Control rods and water reduce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.59,0:29:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒸汽使之增加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steam increases it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.15,0:29:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而上升的温度能够使它降低\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the rise in temperature reduces it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.27,0:30:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是看不见的舞蹈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the invisible dance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.06,0:30:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不产生烟雾和火焰  却能给整个城市供电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that powers entire cities without smoke or flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.89,0:30:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的确很美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it is beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.46,0:30:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一切都正常的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when things are normal.
