Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.06,0:35:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫同志  你是证人  不是公诉人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Legasov, you are a witness, not a prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.32,0:35:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题由我来问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will ask the questions here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.27,0:35:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你当时不在控制室里  那你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you weren't in the room, then where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在厕所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.01,0:36:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.08,0:36:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍缪克同志询问了那晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Khomyuk interviewed everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.76,0:36:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个在控制室里的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who was in the control room that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.35,0:36:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的说法一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They all told the same story.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.59,0:36:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我就知道迪亚特洛夫的命令是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"I knew what Dyatlov ordered was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.37,0:36:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我不照做  他说  我会被开除"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but if I didn't do what he said, I would be fired."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.30,0:36:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列尼德·托普特诺夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leonid Toptunov.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.45,0:36:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在他死的前一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One day before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.97,0:36:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  迪亚特洛夫同志  你当时在控制里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Comrade Dyatlov, you were in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.34,0:36:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下令让他们提高功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You ordered them to raise the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.85,0:36:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.21,0:36:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在休庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Court is now in recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.00,0:36:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.76,0:37:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解切尔诺贝利这地方吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know anything about this town, Chernobyl?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.17,0:37:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not really, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.92,0:37:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分都是犹太人和波兰人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was mostly Jews and Poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.90,0:37:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹太人在大屠杀中被杀害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Jews were killed in pogroms,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.53,0:37:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯大林强迫波兰人离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Stalin forced the Poles out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.58,0:37:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后纳粹来了  把剩下的人都杀死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then the Nazis came and killed whoever was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.69,0:37:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在二战后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But after the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.22,0:37:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们还是搬来这里居住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}people came to live here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.50,0:37:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们知道脚下的土地浸满了鲜血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They knew the ground under their feet was soaked in blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.33,0:38:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.23,0:38:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的犹太人和波兰人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dead Jews, dead Poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.46,0:38:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.15,0:38:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人想过这种事会发生在他们身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one ever thinks it's going to happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.56,0:38:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.46,0:38:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How much time?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.81,0:38:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许一年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.96,0:38:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说这是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They call it a...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.76,0:38:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说这是"慢性疾病"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They call it a "long illness."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.98,0:38:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒没觉得很慢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't seem very long to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.92,0:38:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你和我说过  我也相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you told me, and I believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但随着时间流逝  我以为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But time passed, and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.24,0:38:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不会发生在我身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it wouldn't happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.84,0:38:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虚度了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wasted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.07,0:38:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虚度了光阴却碌碌无为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wasted it all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.40,0:38:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碌碌无为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.24,0:38:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得我第一次打电话给你的那个早上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you remember that morning when I first called you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.87,0:39:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多么漫不经心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how unconcerned I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.92,0:39:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怎么相信克里姆林宫说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe much that comes out of the Kremlin,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.81,0:39:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是当他们和我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but when they told me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.98,0:39:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我负责清理工作时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they were putting me in charge of the cleanup
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.16,0:39:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说事情并不严重  我相信了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they said it wasn't serious, I believed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.51,0:39:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.29,0:39:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们让你来负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because they put you in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.25,0:39:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.12,0:39:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个无足轻重的人  瓦列利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm an inconsequential man, Valery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.32,0:39:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's all I've ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.41,0:39:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾希望有一天我会有所作为  但却没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hoped that one day I would matter, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.36,0:39:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是站在那些大人物身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just stood next to people who did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.91,0:39:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他像我这样的科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are other scientists like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.42,0:39:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们任何一个人都能做我所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any one of them could have done what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.78,0:39:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.22,0:39:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要求的一切  需要的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything we asked for, everything we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.40,0:39:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人力  材料  月球车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Men, material, lunar rovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.57,0:39:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁能做到这些事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who else could have done these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.88,0:40:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们能听到我说的话  但他们只听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They heard me, but they listened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.78,0:40:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的部长和副部长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of all the ministers and all the deputies--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.43,0:40:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及一大群顺从的傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}entire congregation of obedient fools--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.95,0:40:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们错误地派了一个好人来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they mistakenly sent the one good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.15,0:40:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天啊  鲍里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For god's sake, Boris,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.12,0:40:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是那个最重要的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you were the one who mattered most.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.74,0:40:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它真好看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ah, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.38,0:41:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Legasov.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.74,0:41:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是凌晨0点38分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The time is 38 past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.76,0:41:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应堆已经几乎关停了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The reactor is nearly shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.28,0:41:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4号反应堆的操作人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The operators of Reactor 4
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.77,0:41:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走上了一条通往灾难的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are locked on a path that leads directly to disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.95,0:41:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局势已无法扭转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no way to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.92,0:41:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还不知道  但是木已成舟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They do not yet know it, but the die is cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.41,0:42:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在30兆瓦时  氙气仍在不断产生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At 30 megawatts, xenon is still being created,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.88,0:42:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并没有被中和掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but none of it is burning away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应堆被毒素淹没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The reactor is drowning in poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.64,0:42:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更糟糕的是  反应度的热量根本不足以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To make matters worse, the reactor isn't hot enough
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.58,0:42:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生足够的蒸汽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to produce sufficient steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.92,0:42:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个状态安全提高功率的方法只有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only way to safely raise power from this state
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.67,0:42:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在24小时之内慢慢提高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is to do it very, very slowly over the course of 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.84,0:42:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是迪亚特洛夫希望功率马上提升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Dyatlov wants it done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.92,0:42:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫和托普特诺夫只有一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov and Toptunov have only one course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.15,0:42:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们开始抽出控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They begin pulling control rods out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.10,0:42:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下抽出十多根\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dozens at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.70,0:42:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽出一半  抽出四分之三\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Halfway out, three-quarters of the way out,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.26,0:42:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但功率仍然不变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}still, the power does not budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.18,0:42:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们开始把控制棒完全抽出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So they begin pulling them all the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.10,0:42:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四号反应堆有211根控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were 211 control rods in Reactor 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.87,0:42:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫和托普特诺夫完全抽出了205根\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov and Toptunov completely withdrew 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.59,0:42:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住  控制棒是这辆汽车的"刹车"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember-- control rods are the brakes on this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.25,0:43:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,211根控制棒中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of 211 rods,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.08,0:43:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有6根还留在反应堆里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}only six now remain in the reactor.
