Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.11,0:48:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个按钮  它只有一个用途\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there is a button with one single purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.38,0:48:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"紧急停堆"  或立即停止反应堆运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to "scram," or instantly shut down, the reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.87,0:48:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在苏联核反应堆设备中  这个按钮叫AZ-5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In Soviet reactors, that button is called AZ-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.06,0:48:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦按下AZ-5  所有控制棒会立即插入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You press AZ-5, all of the control rods insert at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.41,0:48:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核反应也会立刻停止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the reaction is stopped dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.14,0:48:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.88,0:48:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等什么  列加索夫  说谎啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you waiting for, Legasov? Tell your lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.35,0:48:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫同志  这是你的最后一次警告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Dyatlov, you will not be warned again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.56,0:49:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不然呢  -消停点吧  迪亚特洛夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Or what? - For god's sake, Dyatlov.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.85,0:49:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫已经暴露了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Legasov's already given it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.55,0:49:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他之前就说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.22,0:49:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-迪亚特洛夫同志  -没办法阻止爆炸的发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Comrade Dyatlov. - there was no way to avoid what was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.01,0:49:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他知道内幕  她也知道  -迪亚特洛夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He knows something. She knows something. - Comrade Dyatlov.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.37,0:49:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是什么货色  瓦列利·阿列克谢维奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what you are, Valery Alexeyevich.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.76,0:49:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是个骗子  -今天我们听得够多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're a liar. - We've heard enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.64,0:49:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被告将还押候审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The defendants will be remanded in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.68,0:49:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-本庭...  -我还没说完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Court will-- - I... I haven't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.05,0:49:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有更多证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I still have more evidence to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.06,0:49:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  你的证词已经完整了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not necessary. Your testimony is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.31,0:49:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法官阁下  -本庭休庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Your Honor. - Court is now adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.65,0:49:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明天继续...  -让他说完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We will resume tomorrow with-- - Let him finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.61,0:49:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Shcherbina...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.60,0:49:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他说完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let him finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.04,0:50:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫破坏了所有规则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dyatlov broke every rule we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.02,0:50:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将反应堆状态推向了毁灭边缘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He pushed a reactor to the brink of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.63,0:50:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这么做是因为他确信核反应堆有保险装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He did these things believing there was a failsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.53,0:50:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AZ-5  一个能停止一切反应的按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}AZ-5, a simple button to shut it all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.81,0:50:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在他所制造的情形下  已不存在保险装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But in the circumstances he created, there wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.51,0:50:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急停机系统有个致命的缺陷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The shutdown system had a fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.84,0:50:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在凌晨1点23分40秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At 1:23:40,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.22,0:50:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫按下了AZ-5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov engages AZ-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.03,0:50:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被完全拔出的控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fully-withdrawn control rods
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.62,0:50:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始重新插入反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}begin moving back into the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.02,0:50:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些控制棒是硼制的  硼能减弱核反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These rods are made of boron, which reduces reactivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.79,0:50:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但控制棒的尖端不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but not their tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.78,0:51:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尖端是石墨制  而石墨会加快核反应速率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The tips are made of graphite, which accelerates reactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.57,0:51:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.65,0:51:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.09,0:51:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们的核反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For the same reason our reactors
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.22,0:51:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反应堆安全壳的原因一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}do not have containment buildings around them,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.39,0:51:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西方国家都有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like those in the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.55,0:51:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们的堆芯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For the same reason we don't use
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.91,0:51:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不使用适当浓缩的燃料原因一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}properly enriched fuel in our cores.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.63,0:51:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们是唯一一个核反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For the same reason we are the only nation
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.01,0:51:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用流水冷却  用石墨做缓和剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that builds water-cooled, graphite-moderated reactors
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.37,0:51:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带有正空泡系数的国家一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a positive void coefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.85,0:51:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.57,0:51:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先与堆芯接触的控制棒部份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The first part of the rods that enter the core
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.09,0:51:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尖端的石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are the graphite tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.73,0:51:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当发生接触后  堆芯在持续加剧的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when they do, the reaction in the core,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.90,0:51:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核反应  瞬间激增\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which had been rising, skyrockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.95,0:51:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,液态水的所有分子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every last molecule of liquid water
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.22,0:51:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间汽化为蒸汽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}instantly converts to steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.10,0:52:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得大批燃料管道膨胀并破裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which expands and ruptures a series of fuel rod channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.69,0:52:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些管道里的控制棒已无法再插入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The control rods in those channels can move no further.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.59,0:52:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石墨尖端被固定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The graphite tips are fixed in position,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.19,0:52:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致无止境地加速核反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}endlessly accelerating the reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.12,0:52:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利4号反应堆此时就是个核弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chernobyl Reactor 4 is now a nuclear bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.61,0:52:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凌晨1点23分42秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1:23:42.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.15,0:52:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩罗沃钦科往下看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perevozchenko looks down
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.64,0:52:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那巨大的反应堆钢盖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the enormous steel lid of the reactor...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.10,0:52:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了难以置信的景象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and sees the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.17,0:52:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个重达350公斤的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The control rod and fuel channel caps,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.15,0:52:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制棒和燃料管道盖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which each weigh 350 kilograms,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.28,0:52:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正上下跳动着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are jumping up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.56,0:52:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跑去警告控制室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He runs to warn the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.91,0:52:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他已经无法阻止即将发生的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But there's nothing he can do to stop what is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.15,0:52:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1点23分44秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1:23:44.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.51,0:52:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒸汽鼓破了更多燃料管道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The steam blows more fuel channels apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.14,0:52:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道功率究竟达到了多高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do not know how high the power went.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.06,0:52:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只知道最后的读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We only know the final reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.93,0:52:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4号反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reactor 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.22,0:52:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原额定功率为3200兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}designed to operate at 3200 megawatts,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.17,0:52:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后超过了33000兆瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}went beyond 33,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.35,0:53:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆芯再无法承受如此巨大的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The pressure inside the core can no longer be held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.63,0:53:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终  导致了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At long last, we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.82,0:53:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1点23分45秒的大爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1:23:45, explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.13,0:53:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在反应堆盖子被掀开的瞬间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the instant the lid is thrown off the reactor,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.31,0:53:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧气冲了进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}oxygen rushes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.66,0:53:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与氢和过热的石墨混合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It combines with hydrogen and super-heated graphite.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.49,0:53:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾难链在此时也构建完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The chain of disaster is now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.52,0:53:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Dyatlov!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.35,0:53:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Dyatlov!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.07,0:54:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一晚在控制室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one in the room that night knew
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.99,0:54:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不知道紧急停机按钮相当于引爆器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the shutdown button could act as a detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.91,0:54:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们并不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They didn't know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.83,0:54:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这一点被刻意隐瞒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because it was kept from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.96,0:54:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫同志  这和你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade Legasov, you're contradicting
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.38,0:54:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在维也纳的证词自相矛盾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your own testimony in Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.05,0:54:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在维也纳撒谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My testimony in Vienna was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.59,0:54:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向全世界撒了谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I lied to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.76,0:54:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是唯一一个保守这个秘密的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not the only one who kept this secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.93,0:54:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有许多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are many.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.18,0:54:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都只是服从命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were following orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.89,0:54:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从克格勃  服从中央委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the KGB, from the Central Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.89,0:54:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在  苏联境内还有16个反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And right now, there are 16 reactors in the Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.44,0:54:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着同样的致命缺陷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the same fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.02,0:54:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中三个就在距离切尔诺贝利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three of them are still running
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.78,0:54:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到20公里的地方运行着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}less than 20 kilometers away at Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.57,0:54:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授  如果您的意思是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Professor Legasov, if you mean to suggest the Soviet State
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.49,0:54:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联应对所发生的一切负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is somehow responsible for what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.41,0:55:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我必须警告您  您的立场很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then I must warn you, you are treading on dangerous ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.75,0:55:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经身处危险的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've already trod on dangerous ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.62,0:55:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就在危险的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're on dangerous ground right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.67,0:55:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我们的秘密和谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because of our secrets and our lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.54,0:55:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们几乎定义了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're practically what define us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.71,0:55:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当事与愿违  我们用谎言编织谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the truth offends, we lie and lie
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.97,0:55:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我们忘记真相的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until we can no longer remember it is even there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.26,0:55:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真相就在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it is still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.56,0:55:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每撒一个谎  就欠真理一条债\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every lie we tell incurs a debt to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.94,0:55:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这债  迟早是要还的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sooner or later, that debt is paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.20,0:55:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是RBMK反应堆堆芯爆炸的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is how an RBMK reactor core explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.25,0:55:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.71,0:57:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦列利·阿列克谢维奇·列加索夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Valery Alexeyevich Legasov,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.75,0:57:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲是阿列克谢·列加索夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}son of Alexei Legasov,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:58:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央委员会意识形态合规部部长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Head of Ideological Compliance, Central Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.55,0:58:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你父亲在那里做什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know what your father did there?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.51,0:58:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.85,0:58:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生时期  你是苏共青年团的领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As a student, you had a leadership position in Komsomol.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.18,0:58:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共青团  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communist Youth, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.64,0:58:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-知道还问  -回答问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You already know. - Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.90,0:58:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.98,0:58:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在库尔恰托夫原子能研究所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the Kurchatov Institute,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.24,0:58:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾任党委书记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you were the Communist Party secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.95,0:58:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在位时  限制了犹太裔科学家的晋升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the position, you limited the promotion of Jewish scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.71,0:58:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.21,0:58:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以取悦克里姆林宫官员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To curry favor with Kremlin officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.51,0:58:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我们是一路人  列加索夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're one of us, Legasov.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.26,0:58:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以随意处置你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can do anything I want with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.85,0:58:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我最想告诉你  我很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what I want most is for you to know that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.98,0:58:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.10,0:58:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not heroic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.15,0:59:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是个忘了自己身份的垂死之人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're just a dying man who forgot himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.74,0:59:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我是怎样的人  也知道自己做过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know who I am, and I know what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.87,0:59:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在公正的世界里  我会因为撒谎被枪毙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In a just world, I'd be shot for my lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.24,0:59:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是因为道出了真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but not for this, not for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.79,0:59:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scientists...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.88,0:59:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痴迷于理性的愚蠢执念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and your idiot obsessions with reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.63,0:59:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当子弹击穿你的头骨时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the bullet hits your skull,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.88,0:59:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因还重要吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what will it matter why?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.68,0:59:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会被枪毙  列加索夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one's getting shot, Legasov.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.81,0:59:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在维也纳已经举世闻名了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The whole world saw you in Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.23,0:59:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在杀了你的话会让我们很难堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would be embarrassing to kill you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.40,0:59:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有什么意义呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.86,0:59:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天的证言不会被国家接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your testimony today will not be accepted by the State.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.95,0:59:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会被媒体报导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will not be disseminated in the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.12,0:59:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你根本没说过一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.12,0:59:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你会活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you will live,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.25,0:59:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能活多久活多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}however long you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.25,1:00:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不再是科学家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but not as a scientist, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.09,1:00:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能保留职位和办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll keep your title and your office,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.09,1:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没有工作  没有权力  没有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but no duties, no authority, no friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.64,1:00:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会和你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one will talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.64,1:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没人会听你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one will listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.52,1:00:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他那些不如你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Other men, lesser men,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.11,1:00:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会获得本属于你的荣誉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will receive credit for the things you have done.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.74,1:00:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的贡献现在成了他们的贡献\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your legacy is now their legacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.07,1:00:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会活着见到这一幕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll live long enough to see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.33,1:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳在这件事中扮演了什么角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What role did Shcherbina play in this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.08,1:00:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有参与\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.08,1:00:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他并不知道我要说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He didn't know what I was gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.79,1:00:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍缪克呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What role did Khomyuk play in this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.92,1:00:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也没有参与\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.46,1:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She didn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.30,1:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到你今天的所作所为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After all you've said and done today,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.93,1:00:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你选择现在撒谎就太奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it would be curious if you chose this moment to lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.81,1:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样见多识广的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would think a man of your experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.65,1:01:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该听得出我有没有撒谎吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would know a lie when he hears one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.20,1:01:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能再和他们两个见面或交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will not meet or communicate with either one of them ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.70,1:01:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不能再和切尔诺贝利事件有关人员交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will not communicate with anyone about Chernobyl ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.58,1:01:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将成为一个无关紧要的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will remain so immaterial to the world around you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.00,1:01:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你死去的那天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that when you finally do die,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.54,1:01:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就仿佛你从未出生过一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it will be exceedingly hard to know that you ever lived at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.43,1:01:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.60,1:01:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要担心不会发生的事情呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why worry about something that isn't going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.98,1:01:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"为什么要担心不会发生的事情呢"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Why worry about something that isn't going to happen?"
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.15,1:01:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.69,1:01:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们应该把这句话印在钞票上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They should put that on our money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.81,1:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家都是天真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To be a scientist is to be naive.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.89,1:03:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们过于关注对真相的追寻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are so focused on our search for truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.27,1:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没考虑过鲜有人想让我们发现真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we fail to consider how few actually want us to find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.07,1:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真相就在那里  不管我们是否发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it is always there, whether we see it or not,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.32,1:03:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我们选择看还是不看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whether we choose to or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.37,1:03:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相不会在乎我们的需求或想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The truth doesn't care about our needs or wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.08,1:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会在乎我们的政府  意识形态或宗教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't care about our governments, our ideologies, our religions.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.88,1:03:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会永远在那里等着被发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will lie in wait for all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.50,1:03:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是切尔诺贝利事故留下的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this, at last, is the gift of Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.42,1:03:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经害怕真相的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where I once would fear the cost of truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.97,1:03:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我只会问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}now I only ask:
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.81,1:03:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谎言的代价是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is the cost of lies?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.34,1:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(192,275)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0}瓦列利·列加索夫于1988年4月26日自杀\N享年51岁  当天恰好是切尔诺贝利核泄漏事故两周年整
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.56,1:04:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,269.273)}列加索夫的回忆录录音带在苏维埃科学界流传
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.57,1:04:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,286.454)}他的自杀让这些录音带无法被忽略
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.21,1:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}受其死亡事件的影响  苏维埃官员终于承认\NRBMK反应堆的设计缺陷
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.08,1:04:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}剩下的反应堆都做了改进  \N以防止类似切尔诺贝利的事故再次发生
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.01,1:04:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}在切尔诺贝利事件中\N列加索夫曾获得数十名科学家孜孜不倦的帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.10,1:04:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}有些人公开反对官方的说法\N并因此被告发  逮捕或监禁
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.78,1:04:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}乌拉娜·霍缪克是个虚构角色  代表了他们所有人\N向他们对真相和人类的奉献致敬
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.62,1:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,257)}鲍里斯·谢比纳于1990年8月22日去世
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.13,1:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,276.636)}距他被派往切尔诺贝利已过去4年零4个月
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.30,1:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,286.454)}鉴于他们在切尔诺贝利灾难中所扮演的角色\N维克多·布卡诺夫  安纳托利·迪亚特洛夫  尼克莱·福明被判劳改十年
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.19,1:05:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,257.818)}尼克莱·福明在被释放后
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.16,1:05:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,277.455)}去了俄罗斯加里宁的一座核电站工作
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.99,1:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,261.909)}安纳托利·迪亚特洛夫因辐射相关的疾病\N于1995年去世  享年64岁
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.54,1:05:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}瓦列利·霍登楚克的遗体至今仍未被发现\N他被永远埋在4号反应堆下
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.06,1:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,257)}消防员们穿过的衣服还留在普里皮亚季医院的地下室
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.16,1:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}至今残存的放射量依然很危险
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.24,1:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,286.454)}在丈夫和女儿惨死后  柳德米拉·伊格纳滕科多次中风\N医生告诉她  她再也无法怀孕
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.67,1:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,257)}但他们错了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.09,1:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}她后来跟她的儿子在基辅生活
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.76,1:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,269.272)}那些在铁路桥上围观的人群  据称一个都没有活下来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.56,1:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,285.636)}现在这座桥被称为死亡桥
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.19,1:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,269.272)}400名矿工夜以继日地工作了一个月  防止核熔毁灾难
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.45,1:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,285.636)}据估计其中至少100人没能活过40岁
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.00,1:07:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,285.636)}媒体曾广泛报道称\N潜入水下抽空起泡池的三名潜水员英勇牺牲
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.56,1:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,258.636)}实际上他们经治疗活了下来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.77,1:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,277.455)}有两人甚至活到了今日
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.22,1:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,246.363)}超过60万人被征召去隔离区内做清理工作
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.14,1:07:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,286.454)}尽管其中大批人因为辐射染上了疾病或死亡\N但苏维埃政府没有记录这些人的命运
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.03,1:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}乌克兰和白俄罗斯被污染的地区  也就是"隔离区"\N范围为2600平方公里
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.38,1:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,268.454)}大约30万人被迫永久离开家园
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.30,1:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,286.454)}他们当时被告知这只是暂时的  但直到现在仍被禁止返回
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.73,1:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}米哈伊尔·戈尔巴乔夫一直担任苏联最高领袖\N直到苏联1991年解体
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.86,1:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,285.636)}2006年时  他写到\N"切尔诺贝利的核熔毁事故  或许是苏联解体的真正起因"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.33,1:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,268.455)}2017年切尔诺贝利新石棺终于完工
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.85,1:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,284)}耗费近20亿美元  预计可使用100年
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.23,1:08:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,268.455)}核爆炸事故后  乌克兰和白俄罗斯人民的癌症率骤升
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.20,1:08:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,286.455)}上升最快的人群是儿童
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.29,1:09:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,257)}我们永远无法确切知道切尔诺贝利事故导致多少人死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.50,1:09:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,276.636)}大多数人估计是4000到9.3万人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.97,1:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,256.182)}苏联官方公布的数据  自1987年就没变过
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.48,1:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,275)}是31人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.52,1:09:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\fs18\fn微软雅黑\bord0\pos(192,165.364)}谨以此纪念那些受难和牺牲的人
